timing_all_re..._pins_by_clock(25.10)    timing_all_re..._pins_by_clock(25.10)

Name
       timing_all_registers_filter_clock_pins_by_clock

Syntax
       timing_all_registers_filter_clock_pins_by_clock

       {true | false}

       Default : false

       Reports clock pins filtered based on specified clocks.

       When  set to true, the software will filter and return only those clock
       pins where at lease one clock is from the specified list of clocks.

       This global variable applies only when any of the all_registers command
       parameters, -clock, -rise_clock, -fall_clock, is specified.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

